{"word":"ἀνόνητος","slug":"ἀνόνητος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνόνητος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ὀνίνημι'><el>ὀνίνημι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>unprofitable, useless</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <a href='S:neuter'>neut.</a> <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <el>ἀνόνητα</el> as <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <i>in vain</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>making no profit from</i> a thing, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}